room_title: Escape room "Titanic" by D.O.A. Room Escape in Wisconsin Dells
room_address: 350 E Hiawatha Dr Wisconsin Dells, WI 53965
room_description: It is April 10, 1912 and you are boarding the Titanic for her maiden voyage.  For the first few days it is smooth sailing. On the evening of  April 14, suddenly you hear multiple iceberg warnings!  Then, at 11:40 p.m. the ships warnings start going off ICEBERG DEAD AHEAD!!  You and your fellow passengers must work together to get the massive ship turned in time.  Will you be the one to save the Titanic or will it ultimately sink?
